Insurance

Company Overview of Ayalon Insurance Co., Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Ayalon Insurance Co., Ltd. offers insurance products and services in Israel. The company offers life, health, and general insurance products. It distributes its products through a network of agents and agencies. Ayalon Insurance Co., Ltd. was founded in 1976 and is based in Tel Aviv, Israel. It also operates regional offices in Dan region, Haifa district, Jerusalem district, and Netanya. Ayalon Insurance Co., Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of Ayalon Holdings Limited.


32 Derech Menahem TikvaTel Aviv,  61372IsraelFounded in 1976



Phone: 972 3 756 9210

Fax: 972 3 538 1062

www.ayalon-ins.co.il







