Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Insurance
Sub-Industry: P&C Insurance
Ayalon Insurance Company Ltd. operates as an insurance services firm. The Company offers death, disability, health, illness, car, property, liability, engineering, maritime, land, and contract work insurance. Ayalon Insurance serves customers in Israel.




